{"tid":1017328,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"不只BTS登上葛萊美！韓團出身的他也到了　全英文流利對答","createTime":"2019-02-11T11:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T12:16:56.000Z","uid":3189,"like":6,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f45e4ce8b99ef7087bb9e29ebe8a58aa534c3f4d","tid":1017328,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:09:14.000Z","msg":"記者吳孟庭／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n南韓團體BTS防彈少年團登上葛萊美（Grammy Awards），成為南韓歌手創舉，不過其實紅毯的另一頭也有一位韓星出身藝人，正是以韓團EXO出道的中國藝人張藝興（Lay），他首度出席葛萊美，不需要翻譯全程用英文流利對答，還透露將與美國藝人合作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3888/d3888757.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3888%2Fd3888757.jpg&h=372a0deb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲張藝興踏上第61屆葛萊美頒獎典禮紅毯。（圖／達志影像／美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n張藝興擔任第61屆葛萊美頒獎典禮動感101音樂大使，以大使身分首次踏上葛萊美頒獎典禮紅毯，他坦言「是我的榮幸，能登上葛萊美舞台更是我的夢想，希望未來可以帶著我的創作、我的音樂，在這裡展現給大家。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3888/d3888748.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3888%2Fd3888748.jpg&h=f9710b04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲張藝興在IG上難掩出席葛萊美的興奮之情。（圖／翻攝自張藝興IG）<br />\n<br />\n被問到和哪些西洋藝人合作？張藝興提到了去年和饒舌歌手傑森德魯羅（Jason Derulo）的作品，但遲疑了一下才說「我想要保留一點秘密，想給粉絲驚喜，就不透露更多了。」至於在今天將遇到許多大咖，他許願想合作的藝人清單，包含德瑞克（Drake）、女神卡卡（Lady Gaga）與新竄紅女饒舌歌手卡迪B（Cardi B）等。<br />\n<br />\n第61屆葛萊美獎將於11日晚上9點於Star World中文字幕再現，FOX+也可隨時觀看，此外2月17日下午4點Star World也將安可重播。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://star.ettoday.net/news/1375400\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstar.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F1375400&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu16Cfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=b70ec1b1\" target=\"_blank\">https://star.ettoday.net/news/1375400</a>"},{"pid":"3d08c65994d98c54bed7e71861ae0d3069302897","tid":1017328,"uid":113773,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:10:05.000Z","msg":"咱們中國有一句話叫做『長江後浪推前浪』，我希望EXO用自己努力改寫這後半句話『前浪永遠站在最高的山頂上"},{"pid":"cbc49e2e329f456403756f6e0fd801fc5ac27042","tid":1017328,"uid":223790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:11:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fac7d860331440e29ed73b36bdb21e50d390ca38","tid":1017328,"uid":223790,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:11:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8c1f2d51b6fbd8d3db4aef6a5a5eb5e7f9f13844","tid":1017328,"uid":52073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:11:47.000Z","msg":"冇煩哥?"},{"pid":"dede78da635530eea6f342d615cb57430470353f","tid":1017328,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:11:57.000Z","msg":"大陸哩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03cb9d9b0d6ef12e7da49614a2b403c8eb31857","tid":1017328,"uid":63057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cbc49e2e329f456403756f6e0fd801fc5ac27042","tid":1017328,"uid":223790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:11:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:12:12.000Z","msg":"話哂都係隊友, g chi下la"},{"pid":"112d333205382aa2aad4b3400da71516779d8f0a","tid":1017328,"uid":68678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac7d860331440e29ed73b36bdb21e50d390ca38","tid":1017328,"uid":223790,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:11:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:12:15.000Z","msg":"今次我就撐你啦邊狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7790be35f61e6cfd02f3ebb25f79633954fff2d","tid":1017328,"uid":223790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:13:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a6a98222a5d5a0260febe36dbdb22ea84a221afe","tid":1017328,"uid":113773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cbc49e2e329f456403756f6e0fd801fc5ac27042","tid":1017328,"uid":223790,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:11:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T11:16: